reviewText: Movie is ok, but will not play in computer only blu-ray player.

The movie is not real bad but it is bad  I won't go to much into spoilers but I will tell you they really made a few power ranger jokes but the one goof was with Jason David Franks this movie is to take part where there are dragons and wizards and such ok in one scene on Jason's arm to see his tattoo that says " ONE ARM BANDIT"  and them you see the word TAP  and it you are a fan you know on Jason's arm he has a tattoo that says " JESUS DIDN'T TAP" that is what I seen it is not a bad movie just on great only Jason David Franks  fans will like it
JASON DAVID FRANK!!!!!! If you are a Power Rangers fan or a hard core JDF fan! This movie is for you!
